---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuoteForm from '../components/QuoteForm.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Medicare — Johnny Watts Agency" description="Learn about Medicare options with Johnny Watts Agency. Expert guidance for Medicare coverage in North Carolina.">

  <PageHero title="Medicare" />

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Medicare is the federally provided healthcare insurance. Original Medicare provides for fundamental doctor and hospital costs. However, Original Medicare might not cover some expenses which can result in out-of-pocket expenses when getting treatment.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To ensure that you will not be spending too much on these out-of-pocket expenses, you can get additional insurance coverage.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We have an extensive experience for providing assistance and services to those seeking Medicare plans.
      </p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/medicare-quote/" class="hero-btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3" style="background-color: #06D9FA; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: capitalize; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 30px;">
          Get a Quote
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M190.5 66.9l22.2-22.2c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0L441 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L246.6 467.3c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.2-22.2c-9.5-9.5-9.3-25 .4-34.3L311.4 296H24c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24v-32c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24h287.4L190.9 101.2c-9.8-9.3-10-24.8-.4-34.3z"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Form -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-2">Let's have a chat</h2>
      </div>
      <QuoteForm />
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
